com.day.cq.mcm.landingpage.leadform.creator

Class LeadFormsCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.day.cq.mcm.landingpage.leadform.creator.LeadFormsCreator

  • public class LeadFormsCreator
extends java.lang.Object
    This CTA lead forms handling servlet accepts POSTs to a form begin paragraph but only if the selector "cta-form" and the extension "html" is used.
